  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6512869/" class="title-link">梁啟超《中國近三百年學術史》摘錄 明末清初部分</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6512869"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/66276283/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/66276283/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">六树梨花压海棠</span>
